","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://chainsawman.dog/movie_reze/","overview":"悪魔の心臓を持つ「チェンソーマン」となり、公安対魔特異4課のデビルハンターに所属する少年・デンジ。憧れのマキマとのデートでうかれる帰り道、雨宿りをしていると、カフェで働く少女レゼと出会いー!?"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"链锯人剧场版：蕾塞篇","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"故事延续TV动画的最终章，讲述男主角电次在偶然邂逅的神秘少女蕾塞的庇护下，在快节奏的战斗中，奔向难以预测的命运。  电次，一个少年，与“电锯恶魔”签订契约，化身“电锯人”，成为隶属于公安部魔物对策特别课四课的魔物猎人，与魔物战斗。正兴奋地等待着与心仪的女性、公安部上司玛奇玛约会，却遭遇突如其来的暴雨，不得不在雨中避雨。在避雨的过程中，他邂逅了名为蕾塞的少女。在附近咖啡馆工作的蕾塞对电次露出了和善的笑容，两人迅速成为了好朋友。这次邂逅标志着电次的日常生活发生了重大改变。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - Il film: La storia di Reze","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Denji è diventato Chainsaw Man, il ragazzo con il cuore del demone Pochita, ed è entrato nella Quarta divisione speciale dei Devil Hunters. Dopo un appuntamento con Makima, la ragazza dei suoi sogni, Denji cerca riparo per la pioggia. Lì incontra Reze, una ragazza che lavora in un bar."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man – O Filme: Arco da Reze","runtime":100,"tagline":"Todo mundo quer meu coração de motosserra! E o coração do Denji?!?","homepage":"https://chainsawmanfilme.com.br/home/","overview":"Denji trabalhava como Caçador de Demônios para a yakuza, tentando pagar a dívida que herdou de seus pais, até que um dia, ele é traído e morre. Em seus últimos momentos de consciência, ele forma um pacto com Pochita e essa fusão cria o Homem-Motosserra. Agora, em uma guerra brutal contra demônios, caçadores e inimigos secretos, uma garota misteriosa chamada Reze entrou em seu universo e Denji precisa enfrentar sua batalha mais perigosa até hoje, movido pelo amor em um mundo onde a sobrevivência não conhece regras."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Человек-бензопила. Фильм: История Резе","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Молодой охотник на демонов Дэндзи, который ждал свидания со своей возлюбленной Макимой, попадает под ливень. Укрывшись от дождя, он случайно встречает девушку по имени Резе, работающую в соседнем кафе. Та добродушно ему улыбается, и разговор становится более непринужденным. После этой встречи повседневная жизнь Дэндзи начинает меняться."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"극장판 체인소 맨:  레제편","runtime":100,"tagline":"아무도 모르는, 소녀의 마음","homepage":"","overview":"데블 헌터로 일하는 소년 ‘덴지’는 조직의 배신으로 죽음에 내몰린 순간 전기톱 악마견 ‘포치타’와의 계약으로 하나로 합쳐져 누구도 막을 수 없는 존재 ‘체인소 맨’으로 다시 태어난다. 악마와 사냥꾼, 그리고 정체불명의 적들이 얽힌 잔혹한 전쟁 속에서 ‘레제’라는 이름의 미스터리한 소녀가 ‘덴지’ 앞에 나타나는데… ‘덴지’는 사랑이라는 감정에 이끌려 지금껏 가장 위험한 배틀에 몸을 던진다!"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - The Movie: Reze Arc","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.sonypictures.de/filme/chainsaw-man-movie-reze-arc","overview":"Denji wurde zum „Kettensägenmann“, einem Jungen mit dem Herzen eines Teufels, und gehört nun zu den Teufelsjägern der Spezialabteilung 4. Nach einer Verabredung mit Makima, der Frau seiner Träume, sucht Denji Schutz vor dem Regen. Dort lernt er Reze kennen, ein Mädchen, das in einem Café arbeitet."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man la película -Arco de Reze","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.sonypictures.com.mx/peliculas/chainsaw-man-la-pelicula-arco-de-reze","overview":"En una brutal guerra entre demonios, cazadores y enemigos secretos, una misteriosa chica llamada Reze ha entrado en el mundo de Denji, y él enfrenta su batalla más mortal hasta ahora, impulsado por el amor en un mundo donde la supervivencia no conoce reglas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Людина-бензопила: Резе Арка. Кіно","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Денджі перетворився на “Людину-бензопилу” — хлопця із серцем диявола, і з того часу став частиною 4-го Спеціального Підрозділу мисливців на дияволів. Після побачення з Макімою, жінкою його мрії, Денджі знаходить притулок від дощу. Там він знайомиться з Резе — дівчиною, яка працює в кав'ярні."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Denji pracował dla yakuzy jako łowca demonów, próbując spłacić odziedziczony po rodzicach dług. Gangsterzy dopuścili się jednak zdrady i zlecili jego zabójstwo. Tracący przytomność Denji zawarł układ z Pochitą, ukochanym pieskiem-demonem, który uratował mu życie. W ten sposób połączyli się ze sobą i tak powstał niepowstrzymany Chainsaw Man. Teraz, w samym środku brutalnej wojny między demonami, łowcami i tajemniczymi przeciwnikami, pojawia się tajemnicza Reze. Denjiego czeka najgroźniejsza dotąd bitwa — wywołana przez miłość w świecie, w którym, by przetrwać, dozwolone jest wszystko."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - O Filme: Reze Arc","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"鏈鋸人 - 劇場版：蕾潔篇","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"主角澱治曾是黑幫的惡魔獵人，試圖償還父母留下的債務。後來，他被黑幫背叛、殺害，就在瀕死之際，他與電鋸惡魔波奇塔締結了契約，從此化身為無敵的電鋸人！擁有「鏈鋸惡魔」力量的澱治，在與夢中情人真紀真約會後，遇見了在咖啡廳工作的神秘少女蕾潔。兩人展開了一段充滿愛情卻又危機四伏的故事。在惡魔、獵人與隱藏敵人交織的殘酷戰場上，澱治迎來了他迄今為止最致命的挑戰⋯⋯"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man: The Movie - Reze Arc","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"I en brutal kamp mellan demoner, jägare och hemliga fiender har en mystisk flicka vid namn Reze klivit in i Denjis värld. Nu står han inför sin dödligaste strid hittills – en kamp där kärlek blir drivkraften i en värld där överlevnad saknar regler."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Om de schulden van zijn overleden ouders af te lossen, werkte Denji als duiveljager voor de Yakuza, tot die hem bedrogen en lieten vermoorden. Terwijl hij zijn bewustzijn verloor, sloot Denji’s geliefde duivelshond met kettingzaag een pact met hem en redde hij zijn leven. De twee smolten samen en zo ontstond de onverwoestbare Chainsaw Man. Tijdens een gruwelijke oorlog tussen duivels, jagers en geheime vijanden komt het mysterieuze meisje Reze op Denji’s pad. Gedreven door liefde komt hij voor zijn gevaarlijkste strijd tot nu toe te staan in een wereld waarin alles is geoorloofd om te overleven."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man – Le Film : L'arc de Reze","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://chainsawman.movie/","overview":"Après avoir mit hors d'état de nuire Katana Man, Denji se demande avec l'agitation de sa vie s'il a toujours un cœur. Il va faire la rencontre de Reze, une jeune femme qui semble s'intéresser à lui. Leur relation s'épanouit jusqu'à ce que la vraie nature de Reze se révèle. Il va livrer un combat périlleux guidé par l'amour mais qui sera explosif."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"เชนซอว์ แมน เดอะ มูฟวี่ เรื่องราวของเรเซ่","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เดนจิ ได้พบกับความรักครั้งใหม่กับ เรเซ่ หญิงสาวที่ตัวเขาเองไม่รู้เลยว่า มีเป้าหมายแสนอันตรายแอบแฝงอยู่"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"劇場版『鏈鋸人 蕾潔篇』","runtime":100,"tagline":"心痛爆擊","homepage":"https://chainsawmanmovie.tw/home/","overview":"為了償還父母留下的債務，為黑道打工的惡魔獵人淀治，遭到背叛並慘遭殺害。在意識消散之際，與他感情深厚的鏈鋸惡魔狗波奇塔，與淀治簽訂契約救了他一命，也讓兩人合而為一，從此誕生了所向無敵的「鏈鋸人」。  如今，在惡魔、獵人與潛藏敵人交鋒的殘酷戰爭中，一位神祕少女蕾潔，闖入了淀治的世界。面對史上最致命的對決，淀治將在這個毫無規則可言的生存遊戲中，被愛推向命運的漩渦。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - The Movie: Chương Reze","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tiếp nối series anime chuyển thể đình đám, Chainsaw Man lần đầu tiên oanh tạc màn ảnh rộng trong một cuộc phiêu lưu hoành tráng, ngập tràn các phân cảnh hành động. Ở phần trước, ta đã biết Denji từng làm Thợ Săn Quỷ cho yakuza để trả món nợ của cha mẹ nhưng bị họ phản bội và trừ khử. Trong khoảnh khắc hấp hối, chú chó quỷ cưa máy Pochita (người bạn đồng hành trung thành của Denji) đã đưa ra một khế ước, cứu sống cậu và hợp thể cùng cậu. Từ đó, một Quỷ Cưa bất khả chiến bại ra đời. Giờ đây ở Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Chương Reze, trong cuộc chiến tàn khốc giữa quỷ dữ, thợ săn quỷ và những kẻ thù trong bóng tối, một cô gái bí ẩn tên Reze xuất hiện trong thế giới của Denji. Denji buộc phải đối mặt với trận chiến sinh tử khốc liệt nhất của mình, một trận chiến được tiếp sức bởi tình yêu trong một thế giới nơi mọi người phải sinh tồn mà không biết bất kỳ luật lệ nào."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"דנג'י, עבד כצייד שדים עבור היאקוזה בניסיון לשלם את החוב שירש מהוריו, עד שהיאקוזה בגדו בו והביאו למותו. כשכבר היה על סף אובדן ההכרה, כלבו האהוב פוצ'יטה כרת עמו ברית והציל את חייו, כך התאחדו השניים לגוף אחד ויצרו את \"איש המסור\" הבלתי ניתן לעצירה. כעת, בעיצומה של מלחמה אכזרית בין שדים, ציידים ואויבים נסתרים, נערה מסתורית בשם רזה נכנסת לעולמו של דנג'י, והוא עומד בפני הקרב הקשה ביותר בחייו – קרב המונע מאהבה, בעולם שבו כדי לשרוד, כל האמצעים כשרים."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - La película: El arco de Reze","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Denji trabajaba como cazador de demonios para la yakuza, tratando de saldar la deuda que había heredado de sus padres, pero la yakuza lo traicionó y lo mató. Antes de perder el conocimiento, Pochita, el perro-demonio motosierra de Denji, hizo un trato con él y le salvó la vida. Así se fusionaron, creando al imparable Chainsaw Man. Ahora, en medio de una brutal guerra entre demonios, cazadores y enemigos secretos, una misteriosa chica llamada Reze irrumpe en su mundo y Denji se enfrenta a su batalla más mortífera, impulsado por el amor, en un mundo donde la supervivencia no conoce reglas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man – Η Ταινία: Reze Arc","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Για πρώτη φορά, ο Chainsaw Man κάνει την εμφάνισή του στη μεγάλη οθόνη σε μια επική, γεμάτη δράση περιπέτεια βασισμένη στην εξαιρετικά δημοφιλή σειρά anime.  Ο Denji δούλευε ως Κυνηγών Διαβόλων για τη μαφία, προσπαθώντας να ξεπληρώσει το χρέος που κληρονόμησε από τους γονείς του, μέχρι που η μαφία τον πρόδωσε και τον σκότωσε. Καθώς έχανε τις αισθήσεις του, ο αγαπημένος σκύλος-διάβολος του Denji, ο Pochita, που είχε ως χαρακτηριστικό του το αλυσοπρίονο, έκανε μια συμφωνία με τον Denji και του έσωσε τη ζωή. Αυτό ένωσε τους δύο, δημιουργώντας τον ασταμάτητο Chainsaw Man. Τώρα, σε έναν βίαιο πόλεμο μεταξύ διαβόλων, κυνηγών και μυστικών εχθρών, μια μυστηριώδης κοπέλα ονόματι Reze έχει μπει στον κόσμο του και ο Denji αντιμετωπίζει την πιο θανάσιμη μάχη του μέχρι τώρα, αντλώντας δύναμη από την αγάπη σε έναν κόσμο όπου η επιβίωση δεν γνωρίζει κανόνες."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - Film: Rezina priča","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"U svijetu u kojem vladaju krv, kaos i demoni, u njegov život ulazi zagonetna djevojka Reze – i sve se mijenja. Ljubav, izdaja i brutalna borba za opstanak isprepliću se dok Denji ulazi u svoju najopasniju bitku do sada. Pripremi se. Nećeš znati što te posjeklo."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man filmas: Reze arka","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"„Chainsaw Man - Filmas: Reze Arka“ - veiksmo kupinas nuotykis, kuris tęsia itin populiarų anime serialą. Denžis dirbo jakuzos velnių medžiotoju, bandydamas grąžinti skolą, kurią paveldėjo iš savo tėvų, tačiau jakuza jį išduoda ir nužudo. Vaikinui praradus sąmonę, jo mylimas grandininio pjūklo varomas velniškas šuo Pochita sudaro sandėrį su Denji ir išgelbėja jo gyvybę. Tai sujungia juos abu į vieną būtybę ir sukuria nesustabdomą Chainsaw Man. Žiaurioje kovoje tarp velnių, medžiotojų ir slaptų priešų, į Denji pasaulį įžengė paslaptinga mergina vardu Reze. Kurstomas meilės, jis stoja į kovą, kurioje taisyklės neegzistuoja."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"चेनसॉ मैन दी मूवी: रेज़े आर्क","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man Филмът: Арката на Резе","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Дългове, измама и рискована сделка с дявола – така започва историята на Денджи, младеж, който работи като ловец на дяволи за якудза, за да изплати задълженията на родителите си, до момента, в който мафията го предава и го оставя на прага на смъртта. Докато животът го напуска, верният приятел на Денджи – обичаното му дяволско куче с моторна резачка, Почита – сключва сделка с него, за да го спаси. Така двамата се сливат в едно същество: неудържимия Chainsaw Man. Сега, в брутална война между демони, ловци и скрити врагове, на сцената се появява загадъчната Резе – и Денджи се изправя пред най-опасната си битка…"},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"رجل المنشار: فصل ريزي","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"في حرب وحشية بين الشياطين والصيادين والأعداء السريين، دخلت فتاة غامضة تدعى ريزي عالم دينجي، الذي يواجه أخطر معركة له حتى الآن، مدفوعًا بالحب في عالم لا تعرف فيه البقاء على قيد الحياة أي قواعد."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Denji immár a Special Division 4-hez tartozó démonvadász. Egy esős nap után, miután találkozott Makimával – aki addigra az álmai nőjévé vált –, menedéket keres, és egy kávézóban megismerkedik Reze-zel. Reze a káprázatos szépségű lány, akibe Denji mélységesen beleszeret. Ám Reze nem az, akinek látszik. A romantika és az emberi kapcsolat illúziója tragédiába torkollik, amikor kiderül, hogy Reze valódi céljai megrendítik Denji bizalmát és kilátásait.  (Csillag Lajos)"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man – Filmul: Arcul Reze","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"După ce l-a neutralizat pe Katana Man, Denji se întreabă dacă mai are un suflet în mijlocul turbulențelor din viața sa. O cunoaște pe Reze, o tânără care pare interesată de el. Relația lor înflorește până când se dezvăluie adevărata natură a lui Reze. El se lansează într-o bătălie periculoasă, dar explozivă, alimentată de iubire."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - filma: Reze stāsts","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nežēlīgajā karā starp nelabajiem, medniekiem un slepeniem ienaidniekiem noslēpumaina meitene vārdā Reze ienāk Dendzi pasaulē, un Dendzi gaidāma nāvējošākā cīņa, ko iedvesmo mīlestība pasaulē, kurā izdzīvošanai nav noteikumu."},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - The Movie: Reze Arc","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - The Movie: Reze Arc","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Midt i en nådeløs kamp mellom djevler, jegere og skjulte fiender, dukker en mystisk jente ved navn Reze opp – og Denji kastes ut i sitt livs farligste kamp, drevet av kjærlighet i en verden uten regler."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - The Movie: Reze Arc","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"V brutální válce mezi démony, lovci a tajnými nepřáteli vstoupila do Denjiho světa tajemná dívka jménem Reze a on čelí své dosud nejtěžší bitvě, poháněn láskou ve světě, kde přežití nezná žádná pravidla."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"مرد اره ای: سرنوشت رزه","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"داستان این انیمه که ادامه مستقیم فصل اول انیمه محبوب «Chainsaw Man» محسوب می‌شود، بر اساس آرک «Reze» از مانگای اصلی تاتسکی فوجیموتو ساخته شده و به رابطه‌ی میان دنجی و رزه و رویارویی آن‌ها با خطرات تازه‌ای در دنیای شکارچیان شیطان می‌پردازد..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - The Movie: Reze Arc","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"İblisler, avcılar ve gizli düşmanlar arasında süren acımasız bir savaşta, Reze adında gizemli bir kız Denji'nin dünyasına adım atar ve Denji, hayatta kalmanın kural tanımadığı bir dünyada, aşkla beslenen en ölümcül savaşıyla karşı karşıya kalır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - La pel·lícula: L'arc de Reze","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En una guerra brutal entre dimonis, caçadors i enemics secrets, una noia misteriosa anomenada Reze ha entrat al món de Denji, i ell s'enfronta a la seva batalla més mortal fins ara, impulsada per l'amor en un món on la supervivència no coneix regles."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Chainsaw Man - Le Film : L'Arc de Reze","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Après avoir mit hors d'état de nuire Katana Man, Denji se demande avec l'agitation de sa vie s'il a toujours un cœur. Il va faire la rencontre de Reze, une jeune femme qui semble s'intéresser à lui. Leur relation s'épanouit jusqu'à ce que la vraie nature de Reze se révèle. Il va livrer un combat périlleux guidé par l'amour mais qui sera explosif."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"رجل المنشار: فصل ريزي","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"في حرب وحشية بين الشياطين والصيادين والأعداء السريين، دخلت فتاة غامضة تدعى ريزي عالم دينجي، الذي يواجه أخطر معركة له حتى الآن، مدفوعًا بالحب في عالم لا تعرف فيه البقاء على قيد الحياة أي قواعد."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"6903a46821cb310d389a7d75","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6903a46821cb310d389a7d75","author":"Muhammad Salman","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-10-30T17:46:16.658Z","updated_at":"2025-11-08T23:47:05.961Z","author_details":{"name":"Muhammad Salman","rating":10,"username":"Salman7236","avatar_path":"/91rmcpxyKSvt1K7BHo6G2eQUCmY.jpg"}},{"id":"690dd11f5a6e68d567ce7b59","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/690dd11f5a6e68d567ce7b59","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$12","created_at":"2025-11-07T10:59:43.921Z","updated_at":"2025-11-07T11:03:22.713Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1083637,"adult":false,"title":"Kantara - A Legend: Chapter 1","video":false,"overview":"During the Kadamba reign, King Vijayendra, the ruler of the fictional feudatory land of Bangra, meets his final fate while venturing into the mystical forest of Kantara. Witnessing this, his son Rajashekara seals the borders of their realm. Later, Prince Kulashekara reopens them through a brutal massacre. The protagonist, Berme, in search of prosperity, crosses the divide and ignites a conflict of faith, power, and destiny between the Kingdom and Nature.","genre_ids":[28,18,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":24.5913,"vote_count":60,"poster_path":"/ehQPboTPaIMkMUOoNOh8e7pZ5Rp.jpg","release_date":"2025-10-01","vote_average":7.067,"backdrop_path":"/w57nxiBIODAYHLRs1xmrCY9zEFe.jpg","original_title":"ಕಾಂತಾರ: ಅಧ್ಯಾಯ - ೧","original_language":"kn"},{"id":1186350,"adult":false,"title":"Marco","video":false,"overview":"The adoptive son of the Adattu family, Marco, sets off on a ruthless quest for vengeance after his brother is brutally murdered, finding only betrayal, loss and unimaginable brutality at every step.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.4341,"vote_count":106,"poster_path":"/il3ao5gcF6fZNqo1o9o7lusmEyU.jpg","release_date":"2024-12-20","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/a6RkQIOZ6wThQOEDv6lHsfH53hD.jpg","original_title":"മാർക്കോ","original_language":"ml"},{"id":1010756,"adult":false,"title":"The Strangers: Chapter 2","video":false,"overview":"After learning that one of their victims, Maya, is still alive, The Strangers return to finish the job. With nowhere to run and no one to trust, Maya soon finds herself in a brutal fight for survival against psychopaths more than willing to kill anyone who stands in their way.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.1635,"vote_count":235,"poster_path":"/aEk9jLbiKTVssdATbrF879NvyyJ.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-25","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/AkzGC9vQbKMHGebetpjBF4bU4VS.jpg","original_title":"The Strangers: Chapter 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":639988,"adult":false,"title":"No Other Choice","video":false,"overview":"After being laid off and humiliated by a ruthless job market, a veteran paper mill manager descends into violence in a desperate bid to reclaim his dignity.","genre_ids":[80,53,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":39.6953,"vote_count":719,"poster_path":"/sBpxTGLzKnvPSVtL5yQYpSxvKEb.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-24","vote_average":7.572,"backdrop_path":"/vuUDwAi9UgLyNN9xZLtKTaLQWnl.jpg","original_title":"어쩔수가없다","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1396558,"adult":false,"title":"Bloody Axe Wound","video":false,"overview":"Abbie Bladecut is a teenager torn between the macabre traditions of her family’s bloody trade and the tender stirrings of her first crush. In the small town of Clover Falls, Abbie’s father Roger has built an infamous legacy by capturing real-life killings on tape and selling them to eager customers, but as Abbie delves deeper into the grisly family business, she begins to wonder if it’s time to take the family tradition in a new direction.","genre_ids":[27,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0282,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/dS9sU5JGnkmEVZ9ubgnJa6RMLwx.jpg","release_date":"2024-12-27","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/bVQe2nzhh4AvI3yDu22hDK6fTfo.jpg","original_title":"Bloody Axe Wound","original_language":"en"},{"id":1537366,"adult":false,"title":"Lost in the Jungle","video":false,"overview":"After a deadly plane crash strands four young siblings deep within the Colombian rainforest, a dramatic rescue mission unfolds, uniting Indigenous trackers and the military in a race against time. For the first time ever, this documentay offers the exclusive account of this incredible true story directly from the children themselves and the rescuers who scoured the Amazon rainforest for a grueling 40 days and nights to find them.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6323,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/im9oE8b6yAXNGTVwSYFZ5TmXgkc.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-30","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/q2ouahUiliKZ7A6mQucJjQd59k0.jpg","original_title":"Lost in the Jungle","original_language":"en"},{"id":1295026,"adult":false,"title":"100 METERS","video":false,"overview":"A gifted runner trains a determined but unskilled classmate, unaware he's creating a rival who will challenge him on the track for years to come.","genre_ids":[16,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.8916,"vote_count":69,"poster_path":"/w2pzrRTevXrW3vgIK4CCYaXvtIc.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-19","vote_average":7.775,"backdrop_path":"/hKy4J8jbiOBmSKs0NlcHP1hLWYl.jpg","original_title":"ひゃくえむ。","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1312946,"adult":false,"title":"The Map That Leads to You","video":false,"overview":"Heather is a young woman traveling Europe with friends before starting her perfectly planned life. A chance meeting with Jack sparks an unexpected romance that leads to deep emotional discovery. As secrets and life choices test their bond, her path changes forever.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5352,"vote_count":292,"poster_path":"/uwvKQIjJpC37IEsEj4ZAn1ITyRy.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-19","vote_average":6.541,"backdrop_path":"/5QKddKk1qEe8CwWYpklmKq68uyo.jpg","original_title":"The Map That Leads to You","original_language":"en"},{"id":1244492,"adult":false,"title":"Look Back","video":false,"overview":"Popular, outgoing Fujino is celebrated by her classmates for her funny comics in the class newspaper. One day, her teacher asks her to share the space with Kyomoto, a truant recluse whose beautiful artwork sparks a competitive fervor in Fujino. What starts as jealousy transforms when Fujino realizes their shared passion for drawing.","genre_ids":[16,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.1773,"vote_count":493,"poster_path":"/4f2EcNkp1Mvp9wE5w7HKxcmACWg.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-28","vote_average":8.079,"backdrop_path":"/2okfik8YwzSfdETpT5cUClSiGFO.jpg","original_title":"ルッ