uarely in the crosshairs of both a powerful consortium of villains and the ever-resourceful Interpol, not to mention Batwoman.","genre_ids":[16,28,80],"popularity":1.4581,"vote_count":125,"poster_path":"/iu01cvxs3eLQzra3YNF1pbpXIZa.jpg","release_date":"2022-02-07","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/vD7Lc0xfcsm9sKikq9HbeHRlqjF.jpg","original_title":"Catwoman: Hunted","original_language":"en"},{"id":10370,"adult":false,"title":"Premutos: The Fallen Angel","video":false,"overview":"Premutos is the first of the fallen Angels, even before Lucifer. His Goal is to rule the world, the living and the dead. His son should pave the way for him and appears arbitrary throughout human history and is then recognized as some kind of monster. In the present time, a young man living in Germany begins to suffer from visionary flashbacks - of the lives he lived in the past as Premutos' son! He remembers how he appeared in the middle age, when mankind suffered from pestilence and during WWII in Russia. On his (earthly) father's birthday, a case containing some strange old book and a yellow potion is found in their garden, which was hidden by some peasant in 1943, who experimented with witchery in order to re-animate his deceased wife. Whe the young man gets in touch with the book and some of the yellow potion, he mutates into a monster and awakens an army of zombies, ready to bring back the fallen Angel Premutos and to disturb the little birthday party","genre_ids":[27,35,28],"popularity":0.312,"vote_count":38,"poster_path":"/1KzZKWIGKS30GvtX88BpCPzcWAJ.jpg","release_date":"1997-03-24","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":"/kN2I71yfFRuE8UX7JOelo8jmHX4.jpg","original_title":"Premutos - Der gefallene Engel","original_language":"de"},{"id":10372,"adult":false,"title":"Ewoks: The Battle for Endor","video":false,"overview":"The army of the Marauders, led by King Terak and the witch Charal, attack the Ewoks village, killing Cindel's family. Cindel and the Ewok Wicket escape and meet Teek in the forest, a naughty and very fast animal. Teek takes them to a house in which an old man, Noa, lives. Like Cindel, he also crashed with his Starcruiser on Endor. Together they fight Terak and Charal.","genre_ids":[12,10751,10770,878,14],"popularity":1.6974,"vote_count":340,"poster_path":"/ntgKdekb7xMKscyh2Hei706LBLf.jpg","release_date":"1985-11-24","vote_average":5.425,"backdrop_path":"/xdH8k2O6mpLv4szeLkQGiM1aSOC.jpg","original_title":"Ewoks: The Battle for Endor","original_language":"en"},{"id":10380,"adult":false,"title":"An American Tail: Fievel Goes West","video":false,"overview":"Some time after the Mousekewitz's have settled in America, they find that they are still having problems with the threat of cats. That makes them eager to try another home out in the west, where they are promised that mice and cats live in peace. Unfortunately, the one making this claim is an oily con artist named Cat R. Waul who is intent on his own sinister plan.","genre_ids":[16,10751,37,12,35],"popularity":1.6775,"vote_count":776,"poster_path":"/k4aLupAkHWwHiEDwvqsZFAnUYF.jpg","release_date":"1991-11-21","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/8UpJ8svNnwVtpu8n62vGke8MOJf.jpg","original_title":"An American Tail: Fievel Goes West","original_language":"en"},{"id":10256,"adult":false,"title":"Metamorphosis","video":false,"overview":"In the Seventeenth Century, while Hungary is fighting the Turks, the population of a small village in the Carpathian Mountains faces the evil Countess Elizabeth Bathory, accused of drinking and bathing in blood of virgin women.","genre_ids":[18,14,27],"popularity":0.5468,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/3bjEVcdBm0H7HDqYSxiNc3j0xZr.jpg","release_date":"2007-01-01","vote_average":4.464,"backdrop_path":"/y3BGYpWY8ZUv2kYHmyRhiKQAab3.jpg","original_title":"Metamorphosis","original_language":"en"},{"id":10288,"adult":false,"title":"Fido","video":false,"overview":"Timmy Robinson's best friend in the whole wide world is a six-foot tall rotting zombie named Fido. But 